oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Bill Anderson and the Po' Boys
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Anderson, Bill, 1937-; Gately, Jimmy; Grand Ole Opry (Radio program); Howard, Jan (Vocalist); Martin, Benny; Offset printing;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: A black and white negative taped to and framed by a masking sheet advertising the nationally syndicated Grand Ole Opry Bill Anderson Show featuring Bill Anderson and the Po' Boys, Jan Howard, and Jimmy Gately. The bottom portion of the item is missing. The negative would have been used to create a corresponding printing plate.
